  <entry>
    <title>1. 注释的使用</title>
    <url>/2020/08/16/1.%20%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="注释的使用"><a href="#注释的使用" class="headerlink" title="注释的使用"></a>注释的使用</h1><h2 id="格式："><a href="#格式：" class="headerlink" title="格式："></a>格式：</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> 单行注释：</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 注释内容</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2.</span> 多行注释：</span><br><span class="line">    （<span class="number">1</span>）</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        注释内容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    （<span class="number">2</span>）</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        注释内容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="作用："><a href="#作用：" class="headerlink" title="作用："></a>作用：</h3><ol>
<li><p>是为了对程序进行说明</p>
</li>
<li><p>注释是给人看的，程序不会执行</p>
</li>
</ol>
<blockquote>
<p>在PyCharm中，</p>
<p>​                ctrl    +    /    可以实现快速给代码添加或删除注释</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Python基础知识</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Python基础语法</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>2. 常见的数据类型</title>
    <url>/2020/08/17/2.%20%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="常见的数据类型"><a href="#常见的数据类型" class="headerlink" title="常见的数据类型"></a>常见的数据类型</h1><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> 数字类型：</span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">1</span>) 整数型int：</span><br><span class="line">        e.g. : <span class="number">3</span> <span class="number">4</span> <span class="number">5</span> <span class="number">6</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">-1</span></span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">2</span>) 浮点型float：</span><br><span class="line">        e.g. : <span class="number">1.5</span> <span class="number">2.0</span> <span class="number">3.5</span> <span class="number">-1.5</span></span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">3</span>) 复数complex：</span><br><span class="line">        e.g. : (<span class="number">-1</span>) ** <span class="number">0.5</span></span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2.</span> 字符串类型：（Python里的字符串要求使用一对单引号/双引号包裹）</span><br><span class="line">    e.g. : <span class="string">&#x27;abc&#x27;</span> <span class="string">&#x27;123&#x27;</span> <span class="string">&#x27;你好！&#x27;</span> </span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3.</span> 布尔类型：（用来表示 真假/对错）</span><br><span class="line">    布尔类型中一共只有两个值:</span><br><span class="line">    一个是<span class="literal">True</span>,另一个是<span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">4.</span> 现阶段了解：</span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">1</span>) 列表类型：</span><br><span class="line">        e.g. : names = [<span class="string">&#x27;张三&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;李四&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;王五&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;赵六&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">2</span>) 元组类型：</span><br><span class="line">        e.g. : nums = (<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">3</span>) 集合类型：</span><br><span class="line">        e.g. : x = &#123;<span class="number">9</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;Hello&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">10</span> <span class="string">&#x27;你好！&#x27;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">4</span>) 字典类型：</span><br><span class="line">        e.g. : person = &#123;<span class="string">&#x27;name&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;张三&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;age&#x27;</span>: <span class="number">18</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;height&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;18湖北0cm&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;addr&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;湖北&#x27;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
